{"type": "article", "id": 5660, "title": "尼斯湖怪兽造型的勺子", "description": "", "date": "2015-01-29T08:06:02Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 39, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233828w3Enj8pStLWUBios.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t以色列家居用品品牌 Ototo 最近推出了一款尼斯湖怪兽造型的勺子 Nessie Ladle。设计师为这把汤勺做了 4 条又短又粗的小腿，使其真的像是一只宠物般地可以站立在桌面或是汤锅中。如若是放在盛满汤汁的锅中，Nessie Ladle 仿若探出脑袋一般浮在汤面上，顿时让自己的厨房也变得萌萌哒。定价 15.99 美元（约合人民币 100 元），<a href=\"http://www.animicausa.com/shop/Nessie-Ladle/tpflypage.tpl.html\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233827rBUSzwqH9FijyeLX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.453125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233828b5vVZ3GRA4mDHk02.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6859375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}